message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL", "cs.AI", "cs.LG", "cs.NE", and "cs.IR". This is because the paper discusses the development of a machine learning model using transformers for question generation, which falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), neural networks (cs.NE), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
